2007-07-31  Sancho Lerena  <slerena@gmail.com>

        * util/snmptrapd: Deleted binary.

        * pandora_snmpconsole: Fixed startup scripts. Many checks added to
        manage NetSNMP Trap daemon. Now uses /usr/sbin/snmptrapd by
